snippet: A double suicide attack that killed eight people at a cafe in Tripoli was carried out by the Islamic State group, the interior minister said Sunday.
abstract: Lebanese Interior Min Nohad Machnouk says double suicide attack that killed eight people at cafe in Tripoli was carried out by Islamic State.
lead_paragraph: A double suicide attack that killed eight people at a cafe in Tripoli was carried out by the Islamic State group, the interior minister said Sunday.
